msgstr "Postavitev"

#: webtrees-descendants-chart/resources/views/modules/descendants-chart/form/layout.phtml:29
msgid "Hide the spouses associated with an individual"
msgstr "Skrij partnerje, povezane z osebo"

#: webtrees-descendants-chart/resources/views/modules/descendants-chart/form/layout.phtml:36
msgid "Married names"
msgstr "Poročni priimki"

#: webtrees-descendants-chart/src/Configuration.php:267
msgid "Birth name only"
msgstr "Samo rojstno ime"

#: webtrees-descendants-chart/src/Configuration.php:268
msgid "Married name only"
msgstr "Samo poročni priimek"

#: webtrees-descendants-chart/src/Configuration.php:269
msgid "Birth name with married name in brackets"
msgstr "Rojstno ime s poročnim priimkom v oklepaju"

#: webtrees-descendants-chart/resources/views/modules/descendants-chart/form/layout.phtml:46
msgid ""
"Whether the married name (from a \"MARRIED\" or \"_MARNM\" name entry) is "
"shown — replacing the birth name, appended in brackets after the birth name, "
"or hidden."
msgstr ""
"Ali je poročni priimek (iz vnosa imena vrste \"MARRIED\" ali \"_MARNM\") "
"prikazan — namesto rojstnega imena, dodan v oklepaju za rojstnim imenom ali "
"skrit."

#: webtrees-descendants-chart/resources/views/modules/descendants-chart/form/layout.phtml:53
msgid "Open individual in new browser window/tab"
msgstr "Odpri osebo v novem oknu/zavihku brskalnika"

#: webtrees-descendants-chart/resources/views/modules/descendants-chart/form/layout.phtml:59
msgid ""
"Open the current individual's detail page in a new browser window/tab when "
"it's left-clicked, otherwise the current window/tab is used."
msgstr ""
"Odpri stran s podrobnostmi trenutne osebe v novem oknu/zavihku brskalnika ob "
"kliku z levo tipko miške, sicer uporabi trenutno okno/zavihek."

#: webtrees-descendants-chart/resources/views/modules/descendants-chart/form/layout.phtml:67
msgid "Show alternative name of individual"
msgstr "Prikaži nadomestno ime osebe"

#: webtrees-descendants-chart/resources/views/modules/descendants-chart/form/layout.phtml:73
msgid ""
"Displays a person's alternate name, if available. This simultaneously "
"enlarges the individuals' respective boxes to create the necessary space for "
"the display."
msgstr ""
"Prikaže nadomestno ime osebe, če je na voljo. Hkrati poveča ustrezna polja "
"oseb, da ustvari potreben prostor za prikaz."

#: webtrees-descendants-chart/resources/views/modules/descendants-chart/form/orientation.phtml:22
msgid "Orientation"
msgstr "Usmerjenost"

#: webtrees-descendants-chart/resources/views/modules/descendants-chart/page.phtml:39
msgid "Individual"
msgstr "Oseba"

#: webtrees-descendants-chart/resources/views/modules/descendants-chart/page.phtml:64
msgid "view"
msgstr "Prikaži"

#: webtrees-descendants-chart/resources/views/modules/descendants-chart/page.phtml:75
msgid "Show more options"
msgstr "Prikaži več možnosti"

#: webtrees-descendants-chart/resources/views/modules/descendants-chart/page.phtml:76
msgid "Hide more options"
msgstr "Skrij več možnosti"

msgid "Name abbreviation when space is tight"
msgstr "Krajšanje imena, ko je prostor omejen"

msgid "Automatic (based on tree's surname tradition)"
msgstr "Samodejno (glede na drevesno tradicijo priimkov)"

msgid "Abbreviate given names first"
msgstr "Najprej skrajšaj osebna imena"

msgid "Abbreviate surnames first"
msgstr "Najprej skrajšaj priimke"

msgid "Controls which name part shrinks first when a box is too narrow for the full name. \"Automatic\" uses the tree's surname tradition (Icelandic abbreviates surnames; everything else abbreviates given names)."
msgstr "Določa, kateri del imena se najprej skrajša, ko je polje preozko za polno ime. »Samodejno« uporablja drevesno tradicijo priimkov (islandska tradicija krajša priimke; vse ostale krajšajo osebna imena)."
